import React from "react" const BytonDS = { title: '360° H5 Interactive Tour', client: 'Captive / Byton', media: [ '/resources/digital-solutions/byton/recording.mp4', '/resources/digital-solutions/byton/interior.jpg', '/resources/digital-solutions/byton/popup.jpg' ], body:

Supporting our partner agency, we created a registration check-in system with real-time backend support.

User experience: RSVP for event, generate a QR code for onsite check-in, with prompt SMS reminder service.

Our backend system allows us to make real-time changes and collect data for further use.

 } export default BytonDS
